@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Chinh sach bao mat";
}

<section class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm sm:p-10">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-700">Privacy</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 sm:text-base">
        Chung toi thu thap du lieu can thiet de xu ly don hang, cai thien trai nghiem mua sam va ho tro khach hang.
        Thong tin ca nhan duoc bao mat theo quy dinh hien hanh, khong chia se cho ben thu ba neu khong co su dong y
        cua ban, tru cac truong hop duoc yeu cau boi co quan co tham quyen.
    </p>
</section>
